    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and has plenty of life left for its next owner! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the maintenance, so it's ready to hit the road whenever you are. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great and feels even better behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
