    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double VANOS system. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and an upgraded Bilstein suspension setup that mitigates body roll while maintaining high-speed stability. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal traction during aggressive cornering. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve adjustment and rod bearing replacement, securing the mechanical integrity of the high-revving valvetrain.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
